c":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19972,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/11\/02\/hadith-on-ashura-moses-fasted\/","url_meta":{"origin":6602,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ashura: The day Moses fasted to thank Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to Medina and he found the Jews fasting on the day of 'Ashura. The Prophet said, \u201cWhat is this day you are fasting?\u201d They said, \u201cThis is a great day in which Allah saved Moses and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6859,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/virtues-prayer-parents-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":6602,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Prayer, goodness to parents, jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deed is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in its proper time.\u201d I asked, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood treatment of\u00a0your parents.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/prophet-never-complain-food\/","url_meta":{"origin":6602,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet never criticized food","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would never complain about food. If he liked something, he would eat it. If he disliked it, he would leave it. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3370,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2064 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28177,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-eight-rakaat-forenoon\/","url_meta":{"origin":6602,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Duha: The Prophet prays eight cycles in forenoon","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Hani\u2019 reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace blessings be upon him, in the year of the liberation, and I found him taking a bath. When the Prophet finished his bath, he performed eight cycles of prayer, and that was in the forenoon. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 357,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5952,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/06\/none-say-muhammad-better-yunus\/","url_meta":{"origin":6602,"position":5},"ti